  <h2 id="opportunity-attributes-5" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">Skills and experience</h2>
  
  <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3">Buyers will use the essential and nice-to-have skills and experience to help them evaluate suppliers’ technical competence.</p>
  
  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Essential skills and experience
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>3+ years in a practical DevOps role</li>
          <li>Expert level Kubernetes infrastructure build and operate experience</li>
          <li>Demonstrable experience building secure solutions on Kubernetes at scale, ideally using AWS EKS</li>
          <li>Experience with Istio service mesh</li>
          <li>Experience building secure solutions using Hashicorp tooling: Terraform and Vault</li>
          <li>Able to demonstrate ability to containerise services using best practices</li>
          <li>Can demonstrate practical experience with RedHat/CentOS/Amazon Linux</li>
          <li>Can demonstrate practical experience with containers and container orchestration Experience of managing infrastructure as code, catering for multiple environment differences</li>
          <li>Demonstrable experience of using VCS (Version Control System) in team environments (eg, git, GitHub, BitBucket)</li>
          <li>Demonstrable experience delivering CI/CD pipelines</li>
          <li>Able to demonstrate mentoring colleagues in automation, security, and reliability, within a DevOps context</li>
          <li>Demonstrable experience of identifying manual processes suitable for automation</li>
          <li>Can demonstrate a firm grasp of DevOps and Agile methodologies</li>
          <li>Experience of managing infrastructure as code, catering for multiple environment differences</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Nice-to-have skills and experience
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>Demonstrable experience of Terragrunt</li>
          <li>Worked in a GitOps driven environment</li>
          <li>Able to demonstrate they have worked in regulated environments (eg, finance, government)</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
</dl>

  <h2 id="opportunity-attributes-6" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">How suppliers will be evaluated</h2>
  
  <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3">All suppliers will be asked to provide a work history.</p>
  
  

  

  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          How many specialists to evaluate
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          5
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Cultural fit criteria
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>Be transparent and collaborative whilst working</li>
          <li>Have a no-blame culture and encourage people to learn from their mistakes</li>
          <li>Take responsibility for their work</li>
          <li>Share knowledge and experience with other team members</li>
          <li>Challenge the status quo</li>
          <li>Be comfortable standing up for their discipline</li>
          <li>Be comfortable with working with clients with both high and low technical expertise</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Additional assessment methods
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Evaluation weighting
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-0 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Technical competence</p>
        <div>60%</div>
        <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Cultural fit</p>
        <div>20%</div>
        <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Price</p>
        <div>20%</div>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
</dl>

  </div>
</div>
<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-full">
    

