        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          1. PLEASE NOTE:
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          3 posts are available titled:<br>Dev Ops Engineer – Contract 1<br>Dev Ops Engineer – Contract 2<br>Dev Ops Engineer – Contract 3<br><br>You can submit one candidate on each advert. You can submit a different candidate for each advert or the same candidate for each advert. However If you submit the same candidate on more than one advert and are the top ranked evaluation proposal on more than one contract, then you can only be awarded one contract for that candidate and the next ranked supplier will be offered the contract for the remaining contracts still to be filled.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          2. CV
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          If you wish to send a CV to support your applications, please send it to DS_PMO_Mailbox@disclosurescotland.gov.scot<br><br>(This is optional)
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          3. IR35 Status
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Outside IR35
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
